Best separation strategy
If you want the app to run smoothly, I’d recommend this rule:
•	Static rules go in game-data.json.
•	Domain content goes in one bank per domain.
•	Repeatable logic patterns go in mission-templates.json.
•	Unlockable content goes in separate files.
•	Generated user missions go in their own saved custom bank.
That way:
•	changing XP rules never breaks task content,
•	changing PhD tasks never affects the Skool system,
•	changing boss battles never touches the avatar or shop,
•	generated tasks can be edited independently from official tasks.Memory
